positions:  (5 rows, 3 columns)

header
top-left : top-center : top-right
middle-left : middle-center : middle-right
bottom-left : bottom-center : bottom-right
footer

wallpaper

+--------------------------------------------------------+
|                         header                         |
+--------------------------------------------------------+
|      top-left   |      top-center   |      top-right   |
+--------------------------------------------------------+
|   middle-left   |   middle-center   |   middle-right   |
+--------------------------------------------------------+
|   bottom-left   |   bottom-center   |   bottom-right   |
+--------------------------------------------------------+
|                         footer                         |
+--------------------------------------------------------+


example of left and center (no right):
+--------------------------------------------------------+
|      top-left   |      top-center                      |
+--------------------------------------------------------+
<33%, *>

reverse would happen if it was center and right.
<*, 33%>

example of left and right (no center):
+--------------------------------------------------------+
|      top-left            |                 top-right   |
+--------------------------------------------------------+
<50%,50%>


